housesData.name: House 2
housesData.description: Welcome to this charming house located in a peaceful neighborhood. This spacious home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a cozy living area perfect for family gatherings. With a total living space of 2000 square feet, there's plenty of room for everyone. The beautiful backyard offers a serene retreat with lush greenery and a lovely garden. The house is situated in Mumbai, India and is priced at 50,00,000 INR. For more information or to schedule a viewing, please contact Rajesh at 9876543210.

housesData.name: Villa 1
housesData.description: Escape to this luxurious villa nestled in the picturesque city of Jaipur. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 modern bathrooms, this villa offers a comfortable and lavish living experience. The total living area spans 5000 square feet, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The villa features a private swimming pool, a landscaped garden, and stunning views of the surrounding mountains. It is available for a price of 1,20,00,000 INR. To inquire about this magnificent property, please contact Deepak at 9876543210.
